table.name: ADDRESSES
table.Comment: Street address information for patiens, providers, care sites and pharmacies.

table.Comment: Types of addresses stored in the Address table.

table.name: CARD_TYPES
table.Comment: Type or franchise of credit cards.

table.Comment: Lookup table containing the ISO standard codes for countries.

table.Comment: Source of the ID that connects providers and patients with address and contact information.

table.name: ENTITY_ADDRESSES

table.Comment: Telephone number and type of a person.
